						<h2>Storm, Earth, Fire Abilities<a class="edit" href="/edit/wikibase-article?wikibase_article_id=963">Edit</a></h2>						While Chen is split into the Storm, Earth, Fire Pandas, he has the following Abilities:<br />
<table  style="width:100%;">
	<td  style="background-color:#111111;padding:8px;width:85px;vertical-align:top;">
	
<div class="bbcode_center" style="text-align:center">
<a href="/hots/wiki/abilities/triple-attack">
	<img
		class="ajax-tooltip { t:'WikibaseArticle',i:'1265' }"
		title="Triple Attack"
		src="/images/wikibase/icon/abilities/triple-attack.png"
				style="
												width:75px;
																			height:75px;
																			background-color:#0a0a0a;
																			padding:3px;
																			border:2px solid #080808;
																			border-radius:2px;
																							"
	/>
</a>
</div>

</td><td  style="background-color:#161616;padding:12px;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style="font-size:1.5em"><span style="color:#ffffff">Triple Attack</span></span> <span style="color:#0080ff">(Q)</span><br />
<span style="color:#ffffff">Cooldown: 6 seconds</span><br />
<br />
Order the Spirits to smash the targeted point, dealing <span class="level-scalar" data-stat="ChenTriAttackDamageAmount0" data-base="10" data-gain="4">
	<span style="color:#ffffff">10</span>
	<span style="color:#ddd">
		<abbr title="Increase Per Level">(+4  <small>per level</small>)</abbr>
	</span></span> damage per Spirit alive and slowing enemies in the targeted area by <span class="level-scalar" data-stat="ChenTriAttackSlowUnifiedMoveSpeedFactor" data-base="20" data-suffix="%">
	<span style="color:#ffffff">20%</span>
	</span> for <span class="level-scalar" data-stat="ChenTriAttackSlowDuration" data-base="2">
